Category:Unidentified Jedi of the New Jedi Order

nodes.text: A Defel male was trained as a Jedi in the New Jedi Order. During the Swarm War the Defel was training to become a Jedi at the Ossus Academy. When Chiss Aristocra Chaf'orm'bintrano visited the academy, he was partaking in a game of Skorch, playing as the referee.
